snippet.title: Summer Trip Cruise - Date Announcement Trailer | Wishlist now on Steam!
snippet.description:
Summer Trip Cruise is a game about driving a cruise through the seas and make the tourist have the best holiday of their lives.

Summer Trip Cruise will be released on Steam on May 25th 2023! Wishlist it now and don't miss the release :D

▶Wishlist on Steam! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2103480/Summer_Trip_Cruise/

🕹Developed by Gius Caminiti - 
▶https://twitter.com/GiusCaminiti

🎵 Summer Trip Cruise music by Alejandro Maciá - 
▶https://twitter.com/macia_music
▶https://maciamusic.bandcamp.com/
